{"tid":1482231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【818】欣師我愛你","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:48.000Z","uid":77792,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fc1d60f7cffb06ea2ab857ee9c6e44309cf5e3","tid":1482231,"uid":77792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPZq6Tx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPZq6Tx.jpg&h=91e0ba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c283760c95cf2dfc9e1eb389b13322777913814e","tid":1482231,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ea976d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ea976d0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"8755f753ef8506e4c84f008950293e78a79918bc","tid":1482231,"uid":77792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"818<br />\n818"},{"pid":"68f1565e0d8b270a033af16a105a49e5ac0f7f20","tid":1482231,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"fb5848293c4135bcc48b5e4924f30f0e908a9a9c","tid":1482231,"uid":77792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a4b30e3d17cbdae2293072c46c4008c88fefbedf","tid":1482231,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818 塞爆維園<br />\n<br />\n但其實大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺連登同溫層推無用</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n推就出街推<br />\n<br />\n依度要知嘅全部都知</span></span>"},{"pid":"f493cc2b84068318e74f61f8a80db4daefcbbc9b","tid":1482231,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"Ok 唔恥笑欣師了"},{"pid":"d41e8a2a03bab95dad42e6ca26055615e488c54f","tid":1482231,"uid":77792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"大家行到攰可以上去坐下~"}]}